entries.title: Texas Lawmakers Plan to Further Decimate Abortion Rights in Upcoming Legislative Session
entries.description:
All Texas clinics have halted abortion care, but the anti-abortion movement says its work isn’t over.

The post Texas Lawmakers Plan to Further Decimate Abortion Rights in Upcoming Legislative Session appeared first on The Intercept.

entries.title: Nosso jornalismo tem princípios inegociáveis
entries.description:
O fim do governo de Jair Bolsonaro não torna nosso trabalho mais fácil daqui para a frente. Na verdade, impõe outras dificuldades.

The post Nosso jornalismo tem princípios inegociáveis appeared first on The Intercept.
